                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "is strongly convex, i.e. "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "\\nabla ^ { 2 } f ( x ) \\succeq m I"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "for all "
